description: It's the Smoking Calendar Motorcylce run live from Two Guys Smoke Shop. Motorcycles, cigars, beautiful women, BBQ, and live entertainment - all to support the charities of The Smithfest Foundation as we light up the Brickhouse Maduro and Aging Room Maduro.
